    <h3 itemprop="headline">Florida man charged with murder after allegedly stabbing woman to death in random attack in quiet neighborhood</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Authorities say Kersten Francilus, 25, randomly stabbed a woman to death in a South Florida neighborhood after going door to door asking odd questions.
