    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran's internet blackout hiding strike damage and suppressing dissent, Israeli officials say</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israeli officials say Iran&apos;s internet blackout is hiding war damage, jamming Starlink, and stopping civilians from organizing amid mounting regime pressure.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/03/30/irans-internet-blackout-hiding-strike-damage-suppressing-dissent-israeli-officials-say/"  >(Fox News)</a>
