    <h3 itemprop="headline">Israel approves sweeping death penalty legislation targeting terrorism, EU condemns move</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Israel&apos;s Knesset voted to mandate the death penalty for terrorists convicted of deadly attacks, a shift lawmakers say was driven by the horrors of the Oct. 7 massacre.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/israel-approves-sweeping-death-penalty-legislation-targeting-terrorism-eu-condemns-move/"  >(Fox News)</a>
