  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/tech/2026/04/02/trump-administration-appeals-ruling-that-blocked-pentagon-action-against-anthropic-over-ai-dispute.webp" alt="Trump administration appeals ruling that blocked Pentagon action against Anthropic over AI dispute" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump administration appeals ruling that blocked Pentagon action against Anthropic over AI dispute</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Trump administration is appealing a judge’s order blocking the federal government from taking punitive measures against artificial intelligence company Anthropic after a dispute with the Pentagon over military use of AI.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/02/trump-administration-appeals-ruling-that-blocked-pentagon-action-against-anthropic-over-ai-dispute/"  >(Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
