    <h3 itemprop="headline">Claude Code leak puts enterprise trust at risk as security, governance concerns mount</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Anthropic likes to talk about safety. It even risked the ire of the US Department of Defense (also known as the Department of War) over it.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/03/claude-code-leak-puts-enterprise-trust-at-risk-as-security-governance-concerns-mount/"  >(Info World)</a>
