    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google Research touts memory-compression breakthrough for AI processing</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Memory prices are falling, and stock prices of memory companies took a hit, following news from Google Research of a breakthrough that will greatly reduce the amount of memory needed for AI processing.
AI is notorious not only for processing requirements but also for high memory requirements.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/02/google-research-talks-compression-technology-it-says-will-greatly-reduce-memory-needed-for-ai-processing/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
