        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">New tool on AWS makes it easier to develop quantum error correction</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Google just moved up its timeline for quantum computers to 2029 because of improvements in quantum computer hardware, quantum error correction, and algorithms.
In 2019, Google estimated it would take 20 million qubits to break RSA encryption.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2026/04/02/new-tool-on-aws-makes-it-easier-to-develop-quantum-error-correction/"  >(Network World)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
