      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/03/holocaust-survivor-86-priced-out-nyc-says-mamdani-skipped-scheduled-housing-meeting.webp" alt="Holocaust survivor, 86, priced out of NYC says Mamdani skipped scheduled housing meeting" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
