    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Holocaust survivor, 86, priced out of NYC says Mamdani skipped scheduled housing meeting</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An 86-year-old Holocaust survivor says NYC Mayor Zohran Mamdani failed to follow through on a promised housing meeting as costs soar.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/03/holocaust-survivor-86-priced-out-nyc-says-mamdani-skipped-scheduled-housing-meeting/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:00:49 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:00:49 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static14/politics/2026/04/03/colorado-lawyers-say-court-e-file-system-now-makes-them-certify-wont-assist-ice.webp" alt="Colorado lawyers say court e-file system now makes them certify they won&#8217;t assist ICE" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Colorado lawyers say court e-file system now makes them certify they won&#8217;t assist ICE</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Colorado reportedly requires lawyers to certify they won&apos;t assist ICE as a condition for accessing the state&apos;s court e-filing system, sparking outrage.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2026/04/03/colorado-lawyers-say-court-e-file-system-now-makes-them-certify-wont-assist-ice/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
